videos.description: Jamal Murray attacks the basket, but Kawhi Leonard rises to the occasion to stuff the dunk using his middle finger.

videos.description: Despite having a highly productive night on offense for the Clippers, Paul George tells the media that he must do a better job of providing support on the defensive end to back up Kawhi Leonard.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (George acknowledges he must provide more support to Kawhi) 2020/09/07
